{"tid":1488270,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Can we trade all liberals who burn our flag for HongKongers?","createTime":"2019-08-19T14:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T13:31:12.000Z","uid":52090,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9ccf746563798557a3a963ab8f03688d1f20a123","tid":1488270,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:46:03.000Z","msg":"真攬炒，全球反中<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">No more MADE IN CHINA<br />\nNo more Chinese immigrants</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OiVQlakoUig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOiVQlakoUig&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAPjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=ee89bde2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OiVQlakoUig</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCan we trade all the liberals who burn our flag for the people of Hong Kong?<br />\n燒美國國旗嘅自由主義者可以同香港人交換嗎？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSend Antifa/Democrats to Communist China and import the beautiful people of Hong Kong here.<br />\n送民主黨支持者去中共，換高尚嘅香港人番黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBritain will be back my friends. Give us time to leave the EU.<br />\n朋友，英國會回來，比多少少時間我地脫歐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nThese people would make excellent immigrants.<br />\n歡迎移民黎美國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMy heart goes out to all the freedom fighters risking their lives and livelihoods in Hong Kong right now. <br />\n為所有賭上生命同前途奮鬥嘅香港人，為佢地嘅家而努力嘅人吶喊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCan we send all the Antifa fools to China in exchange for the wonderful people of Hong Kong?<br />\n可以用左膠去同中國交換香港人嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPrayers for Hong Kong and its people! ❤ From U.S.A. !<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為香港禱告<br />\n<br />\nAll I see are beautiful people. God bless the people of Hong Kong.<br />\n我見到好多高尚嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，希望神保𧙗香港人<br />\n<br />\nTo The People Of Hong Kong You Got My Support. Greetings From A Fellow American.<br />\n致香港人：我支持你地，來自美國嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWe all should support HK independence in the West. Shame on those who don't. Avi we love you ! Blessings from Holland !<br />\n我地所有西方社會都應該支援香港獨立，以不發聲嘅人為恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。我愛你地，來自荷蘭嘅祝褔 <br />\n<br />\nI'm so sad about this. Hong Kongers are always welcome in my country, to hell with it, even my house! Us czechs know very well what it is like to be oppressed by a communist dictatorship! Much love to Hong Kong and stay strong!<br />\n睇到好傷心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 歡迎香港人黎我地嘅國家，甚至係我屋企。作為一個捷克人，我好明白獨裁嘅共產政權係點殘害人民。我好鍾意香港，香港人加油"},{"pid":"e31ffcb21e2cf2916b54d0ac804f1fe3a8cb59d1","tid":1488270,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:46:43.000Z","msg":"真攬炒，全球反中<br />\nNo MADE IN CHINA<br />\nNo Chinese immigrants"},{"pid":"57ae257a864ac8f3ca1654c62ca16a4ad1d5a56c","tid":1488270,"uid":206827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:46:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">阻阻大家 入黎擺低死線唔該<br />\n既然無死線做唔到野就擺低死線既日期出黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家個個話要死線 死線呢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488086</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fbcf4548430eedf92fcdd0bc372b1c8cab27a80b","tid":1488270,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:47:50.000Z","msg":"[相似的歷史] 今日台灣，明日香港。台灣由獨裁到民主